/* COMPILER/BOOT/motion_main.iii -- iii motion: GAMMA-MOTION standing, and THE
 * KINETIC SCROLL speaking.  The exact time-of-impact (exact_motion), the
 * constructible tower (pyrgos), the event fold that chains THROUGH irrational
 * impacts (kinesis), and the EIDOLOS voice that states the fold as causal
 * claims and lets the language DERIVE what physics implied.
 *
 *   iii motion prove       the full self-proof (arms 170..179 + 180..187 + 190..196)
 *   iii motion toi     <14 ints>   one pair: HIT/GRAZE/MISS + the exact TOI
 *   iii motion respond <14 ints>   one pair: exact elastic response
 *   iii motion scroll      the irrational chain folded PAST its surds (nested tower)
 *   iii motion echo        the Loschmidt echo: exact return to the integer genesis
 *   iii motion speak       the scroll as EIDOLOS claims; the mirror law DERIVES
 *                          the echo causality the fold never stated
 *
 * Every verb self-proves all three organs first (exit 9).
 * exit: 0 ok | 1 miss | 3 usage | 9 SELF-REFUSED */
module motion_main

